name: nw_ethernet_channel_state_t
desc: States indicating whether an Ethernet channel is able to send and receive frames.

items.name: var nw_ethernet_channel_state_waiting: nw_ethernet_channel_state_t
items.desc: The channel is waiting for its interface to become available.

items.name: var nw_ethernet_channel_state_preparing: nw_ethernet_channel_state_t
items.desc: The channel is registering with the interface.

items.name: var nw_ethernet_channel_state_ready: nw_ethernet_channel_state_t
items.desc: The channel is able to send and receive Ethernet frames.

items.name: var nw_ethernet_channel_state_failed: nw_ethernet_channel_state_t
items.desc: The channel has encountered a fatal error.
